name: SVGFETurbulenceElement
description: The SVGFETurbulenceElement interface corresponds to the <feTurbulence> element.

members.name: SVGFETurbulenceElement.baseFrequencyX
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the X component of the baseFrequency attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFETurbulenceElement.baseFrequencyY
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the Y component of the baseFrequency attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFETurbulenceElement.numOctaves
members.description: An SVGAnimatedInteger corresponding to the numOctaves attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFETurbulenceElement.seed
members.description: An SVGAnimatedNumber corresponding to the seed attribute of the given element.

members.name: SVGFETurbulenceElement.stitchTiles
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the stitchTiles attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_STITCHTYPE_* constants defined on this interface.

members.name: SVGFETurbulenceElement.type
members.description: An SVGAnimatedEnumeration corresponding to the type attribute of the given element. It takes one of the SVG_TURBULENCE_TYPE_* constants defined on this interface.
